notes:
The software is impressive. Feels like a native Apple app. I used my lat Pulldown instead of the functional trainer for the one arm pull downs. 

Do you fee like the Pallof press is a good use of time? I’ve done them a few times, but I never feel like they do much. I understand the anti rotation portion, but I guess they just don’t feel very useful. Would like to hear your thoughts.
